Actress Nancy Isime has reacted to allegations that she’s having an affair with a married UK businessman. Some blogs alleged the actress- cum- show host was enjoying an amorous relationship with the married man, who they said is the source of her wealth. Isime admitted to knowing the businessman but denied having any romantic affair with him, saying they were business partners.   Historic Burna Boy becomes first Nigerian to sell out Accor…     Russian strike kills another Ukrainian film star     Flamboyant social media lifestyle doesn’t translate to…   “Ahn Ahn. Oba of life! Why I nor go come here? Nor be vawulence nation? You nor want make I follow gather? Deny Mr Michael Dion Goli? Abeg read inside these comments make you see where I write am,” she wrote. Continuing, she wrote: “Naim company UK Dion be the headline sponsors of my show TNIS season three. Na me even host their new office launch. I even invite am and e family for my birthday.”